Class VJoyReinit

  • java.lang.Object
    • VJoy.VJoyReinit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class VJoyReinit
extends Object
implements Runnable
    The reinitialization thread for VJoy driver. Due to nature of limitations in the driver, it requires reinitialization every 5 minutes. This thread deals with that.
